index_terms: DEPARTMENT OF SOCIAL AND HEALTH SERVICES
summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Public Health Department; authorizing an agreement with the State of Washington, Department of Social and Health Services for reimbursement to the City of costs for the provision of family planning services; establishing three new positions and increasing certain objects of expenditure in the 1976 Budget of said Department; making a reimbursable expenditure from the Emergency Fund and declaring the Emergency therefor.
